            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Daniel.5:1-31",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EDaniel%205%3A1-31%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_1%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EDaniel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Writing%20on%20the%20Wall%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EMany%20years%20later%20King%20Belshazzar%20gave%20a%20great%20feast%20for%201%2C000%20of%20his%20nobles%2C%20and%20he%20drank%20wine%20with%20them.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_2%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EWhile%20Belshazzar%20was%20drinking%20the%20wine%2C%20he%20gave%20orders%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20gold%20and%20silver%20cups%20that%20his%20predecessor%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E5%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Aramaic%20%3Cem%3Efather%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%205%3A11%2C%2013%2C%2018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Nebuchadnezzar%2C%20had%20taken%20from%20the%20Temple%20in%20Jerusalem.%20He%20wanted%20to%20drink%20from%20them%20with%20his%20nobles%2C%20his%20wives%2C%20and%20his%20concubines.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_3%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20they%20brought%20these%20gold%20cups%20taken%20from%20the%20Temple%2C%20the%20house%20of%20God%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20and%20the%20king%20and%20his%20nobles%2C%20his%20wives%2C%20and%20his%20concubines%20drank%20from%20them.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_4%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EWhile%20they%20drank%20from%20them%20they%20praised%20their%20idols%20made%20of%20gold%2C%20silver%2C%20bronze%2C%20iron%2C%20wood%2C%20and%20stone.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_5%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3ESuddenly%2C%20they%20saw%20the%20fingers%20of%20a%20human%20hand%20writing%20on%20the%20plaster%20wall%20of%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20palace%2C%20near%20the%20lampstand.%20The%20king%20himself%20saw%20the%20hand%20as%20it%20wrote%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_6%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20his%20face%20turned%20pale%20with%20fright.%20His%20knees%20knocked%20together%20in%20fear%20and%20his%20legs%20gave%20way%20beneath%20him.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_7%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20shouted%20for%20the%20enchanters%2C%20astrologers%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E5%3A7%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3EChaldeans%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%205%3A11.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20fortune-tellers%20to%20be%20brought%20before%20him.%20He%20said%20to%20these%20wise%20men%20of%20Babylon%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhoever%20can%20read%20this%20writing%20and%20tell%20me%20what%20it%20means%20will%20be%20dressed%20in%20purple%20robes%20of%20royal%20honor%20and%20will%20have%20a%20gold%20chain%20placed%20around%20his%20neck.%20He%20will%20become%20the%20third%20highest%20ruler%20in%20the%20kingdom!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_8%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20when%20all%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20wise%20men%20had%20come%20in%2C%20none%20of%20them%20could%20read%20the%20writing%20or%20tell%20him%20what%20it%20meant.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_9%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20king%20grew%20even%20more%20alarmed%2C%20and%20his%20face%20turned%20pale.%20His%20nobles%2C%20too%2C%20were%20shaken.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_10%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20when%20the%20queen%20mother%20heard%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20she%20hurried%20to%20the%20banquet%20hall.%20She%20said%20to%20Belshazzar%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BLong%20live%20the%20king!%20Don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20be%20so%20pale%20and%20frightened.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_11%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20man%20in%20your%20kingdom%20who%20has%20within%20him%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20holy%20gods.%20During%20Nebuchadnezzar%26%23x2019%3Bs%20reign%2C%20this%20man%20was%20found%20to%20have%20insight%2C%20understanding%2C%20and%20wisdom%20like%20that%20of%20the%20gods.%20Your%20predecessor%2C%20the%20king%26%23x2014%3Byour%20predecessor%20King%20Nebuchadnezzar%26%23x2014%3Bmade%20him%20chief%20over%20all%20the%20magicians%2C%20enchanters%2C%20astrologers%2C%20and%20fortune-tellers%20of%20Babylon.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_12%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20man%20Daniel%2C%20whom%20the%20king%20named%20Belteshazzar%2C%20has%20exceptional%20ability%20and%20is%20filled%20with%20divine%20knowledge%20and%20understanding.%20He%20can%20interpret%20dreams%2C%20explain%20riddles%2C%20and%20solve%20difficult%20problems.%20Call%20for%20Daniel%2C%20and%20he%20will%20tell%20you%20what%20the%20writing%20means.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_13%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EDaniel%20Explains%20the%20Writing%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Daniel%20was%20brought%20in%20before%20the%20king.%20The%20king%20asked%20him%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BAre%20you%20Daniel%2C%20one%20of%20the%20exiles%20brought%20from%20Judah%20by%20my%20predecessor%2C%20King%20Nebuchadnezzar%3F%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_14%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20have%20heard%20that%20you%20have%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20gods%20within%20you%20and%20that%20you%20are%20filled%20with%20insight%2C%20understanding%2C%20and%20wisdom.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_15%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EMy%20wise%20men%20and%20enchanters%20have%20tried%20to%20read%20the%20words%20on%20the%20wall%20and%20tell%20me%20their%20meaning%2C%20but%20they%20cannot%20do%20it.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_16%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20am%20told%20that%20you%20can%20give%20interpretations%20and%20solve%20difficult%20problems.%20If%20you%20can%20read%20these%20words%20and%20tell%20me%20their%20meaning%2C%20you%20will%20be%20clothed%20in%20purple%20robes%20of%20royal%20honor%2C%20and%20you%20will%20have%20a%20gold%20chain%20placed%20around%20your%20neck.%20You%20will%20become%20the%20third%20highest%20ruler%20in%20the%20kingdom.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_17%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EDaniel%20answered%20the%20king%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BKeep%20your%20gifts%20or%20give%20them%20to%20someone%20else%2C%20but%20I%20will%20tell%20you%20what%20the%20writing%20means.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_18%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EYour%20Majesty%2C%20the%20Most%20High%20God%20gave%20sovereignty%2C%20majesty%2C%20glory%2C%20and%20honor%20to%20your%20predecessor%2C%20Nebuchadnezzar.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_19%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20made%20him%20so%20great%20that%20people%20of%20all%20races%20and%20nations%20and%20languages%20trembled%20before%20him%20in%20fear.%20He%20killed%20those%20he%20wanted%20to%20kill%20and%20spared%20those%20he%20wanted%20to%20spare.%20He%20honored%20those%20he%20wanted%20to%20honor%20and%20disgraced%20those%20he%20wanted%20to%20disgrace.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_20%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20when%20his%20heart%20and%20mind%20were%20puffed%20up%20with%20arrogance%2C%20he%20was%20brought%20down%20from%20his%20royal%20throne%20and%20stripped%20of%20his%20glory.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_21%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20was%20driven%20from%20human%20society.%20He%20was%20given%20the%20mind%20of%20a%20wild%20animal%2C%20and%20he%20lived%20among%20the%20wild%20donkeys.%20He%20ate%20grass%20like%20a%20cow%2C%20and%20he%20was%20drenched%20with%20the%20dew%20of%20heaven%2C%20until%20he%20learned%20that%20the%20Most%20High%20God%20rules%20over%20the%20kingdoms%20of%20the%20world%20and%20appoints%20anyone%20he%20desires%20to%20rule%20over%20them.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_22%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYou%20are%20his%20successor%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E5%3A22%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Aramaic%20%3Cem%3Eson.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20O%26%23xA0%3BBelshazzar%2C%20and%20you%20knew%20all%20this%2C%20yet%20you%20have%20not%20humbled%20yourself.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_23%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20you%20have%20proudly%20defied%20the%20Lord%20of%20heaven%20and%20have%20had%20these%20cups%20from%20his%20Temple%20brought%20before%20you.%20You%20and%20your%20nobles%20and%20your%20wives%20and%20concubines%20have%20been%20drinking%20wine%20from%20them%20while%20praising%20gods%20of%20silver%2C%20gold%2C%20bronze%2C%20iron%2C%20wood%2C%20and%20stone%26%23x2014%3Bgods%20that%20neither%20see%20nor%20hear%20nor%20know%20anything%20at%20all.%20But%20you%20have%20not%20honored%20the%20God%20who%20gives%20you%20the%20breath%20of%20life%20and%20controls%20your%20destiny!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_24%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20God%20has%20sent%20this%20hand%20to%20write%20this%20message.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_25%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20the%20message%20that%20was%20written%3A%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3EMene%2C%20Mene%2C%20Tekel%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3EParsin%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_5_26%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%